    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped out at MRL 2 with documented justification. Output comparison achieves MRL 3 quality (NRMSE 6.8%, NIH within 12%). The assessment team concludes that the CFD model provides adequate credibility for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device and supports pre-market submission. Decision: Accepted.",
